---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Marquis — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Marquis deployed two automated palletizers in under three days, cutting palletizing labor cost ~40% and moving people to higher-value work on its 3,800-acre renewable-ethanol campus."
  ogTitle="Marquis — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="2 systems · under 3 days · ~40% lower palletizing labor cost"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/marquis" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Marquis
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Marquis</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Innovation in Their DNA: Marquis Automates Palletizing to Drive Efficiency and Support Employee Well-Being</h1>
    <p class="lede">Marquis — a multi-generational enterprise producing 395 million gallons of renewable ethanol on a 3,800-acre central-Illinois campus — deployed two automated palletizers in under three days, cutting palletizing labor cost ~40% and moving people to higher-value work.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/marquis-hero.jpg" alt="Marquis automated palletizing cell" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Marquis · central Illinois</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1975</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Central Illinois</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Renewable ethanol</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Employees</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">450</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Annual output</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">395M gal ethanol</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Campus</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">3,800 acres</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why Automation</div>
      <h2>Pay people well. <em>Then free them up.</em></h2>
      <p>Founded in 1975 as a family grain-hauling business, Marquis has grown into nine businesses on a 3,800-acre central-Illinois campus with 450 employees and 395 million gallons of annual ethanol production. Palletizing meant continuous bending, lifting, and turning of heavy boxes — and Marquis pays roughly 40% more than competitors for that same job. Leadership wanted that talent thinking and creating, not stacking.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>~40% higher wages than competitors for the same role</li>
        <li>Continuous heavy-box bending, lifting, and turning</li>
        <li>Goal: use people's full potential, not their backs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/marquis-2.jpg" alt="Marquis production and palletizing line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Palletizing · automated</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic robotic palletizing system" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Reliable · repeatable</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Why Full Service</div>
      <h2>Two systems, <em>under three days</em>.</h2>
      <p>After months of planning, Marquis chose Formic for reliability and repeatability. Both automated palletizing systems were fully deployed in under three days — including training the team — in what the company called one of the smoothest automation transitions it had ever run.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Two automated palletizing systems</li>
        <li>Fully deployed in under three days, training included</li>
        <li>Reliable, repeatable performance was the deciding factor</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"We probably pay 40% higher than most of our competitors in the same space to perform the same job. So we wanted to make sure that the jobs we had folks performing utilized their full potential for thought, creativity, and the ability to think on their feet."</blockquote>
      <cite>Alan VanDuyne · Vice President, Marquis</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Aligned with <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Safety, Honesty, Excellence.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">2</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Palletizing systems</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">~40%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Lower palletizing labor cost</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">&lt;3</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Days to deploy</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Put innovation <em>on the line</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
